{"tid":1440130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急]大家冇晒士氣,要一首歌振奮人心的歌","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T20:55:46.000Z","uid":298610,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f74546ba93079f94f33ae47e1f78f9bdf3de9981","tid":1440130,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:46:49.000Z","msg":"我之前都出過POST想唱國來表示我唔係港獨同愛國,話比上面13億人同拉攏埋D藍屍,但我發現都有一部分覺得唔好含中國撚,寧願站著死都唔要跪住生存,小弟有幾個方案同分析,大家比下意見同幫我推上頂,<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">私心推薦古巨基的追夢者</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n你聽完一次唔心痛就劣評我<br />\n收集完意見我會搞個投票</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文章下面有分析,請認真比意見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1)英國國歌<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yNNYTbJD1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0yNNYTbJD1o&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=0c0ac0b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yNNYTbJD1o</a><br />\n2)美國國歌<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TGOPzKh7jVQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTGOPzKh7jVQ&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=3f7cbb4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TGOPzKh7jVQ</a><br />\n3)中國國歌(我建議改廣東話歌詞)<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5810J8TJ7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq5810J8TJ7c&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=66567266\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5810J8TJ7c</a><br />\n4)十架犧牲的愛 廣東話詩歌- <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sh4wV3nsNPs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSh4wV3nsNPs&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=7847d5ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sh4wV3nsNPs</a><br />\n5)追夢者 造王者主題曲 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NjkXtjTyNMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNjkXtjTyNMI&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=8959b79a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NjkXtjTyNMI</a><br />\n6)THE DAY 我的英雄學院 OP1 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ge0iNhkZNgA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dge0iNhkZNgA&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=aef550e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ge0iNhkZNgA</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1)英國國歌</span><br />\n優點:我地話晒英國殖民地,再加個歌詞<span style=\"color: green;\">GOD SAVE HONG KONG</span>,比較貼切主題,英國聽到都唔可  以唔比反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺點:英國人聽到都冇力幫手,自己都搞緊脫歐自身難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">2)美國國歌</span><br />\n優點:唱比侵侵聽,美國聽到都唔可以唔比反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以迫習大大同侵侵反檯<br />\n缺點:同今次主題唔多岩KEY,同埋侵侵係敵人定係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3)中國國歌</span><br />\n優點:咁多首歌最貼切,因為係革命歌!可拉攏部分藍屍!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起來！不願做<span style=\"color: red;\">奴隸</span>的人們！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>民族到了最危險的時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: green;\"> 冒着警察煙冒彈，前進！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺點:有奶共之嫌,有部分人抗拒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">4)最屈機詩歌</span><br />\n優點:世界2/3人都係信天主基督,勢力比美國還要強,中共同基督徙林鄭都要投降<br />\n缺點:首歌唔多岩主題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">5)追夢者 個人最愛,最鼓舞士氣</span><br />\n優點:劇集係革命片,唱比林鄭聽,主題非常貼切 ,<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我沒有 放不低的散聚<br />\n捍衛我 要堅守的壯舉<br />\n我沒有 過不到的畏懼<br />\n無視那 誣蔑我的判罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">消失的證據 未曾磨滅著過去</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">仍執著一個信念無論結果撐下去<br />\n血脈未靜似水 怎會絕望疲累</span></span><br />\n句句都聽到我好心痛</span><br />\n缺點:CCTVB劇集<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">6)THE DAY</span><br />\n優點:主題貼切,節奏澎湃,建議聽下先嘴我炮<br />\n缺點:日文........"},{"pid":"5b10ee5189907a38f3bdcc6b995ac77d402f3ebe","tid":1440130,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"我推!!"},{"pid":"91be4abc1ac3a9d4665726edb4ec43137182d106","tid":1440130,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:00:10.000Z","msg":"推林鄭老母!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fd0568108bfd6f90c947d28e79c81cf24c0219","tid":1440130,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"全部都唔係好掂喎ching"},{"pid":"7500799967d8706f942796d7352038186959589c","tid":1440130,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5793e2bcaee906725b26cdb58ce2e84518b4d0ff","tid":1440130,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d3fd0568108bfd6f90c947d28e79c81cf24c0219","tid":1440130,"uid":50901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"全部都唔係好掂喎ching"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:27:58.000Z","msg":"多謝指教,你全BAN 都係一個選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada8ae5fcfba0ca7076feccb687a0b92849b4407","tid":1440130,"